ygData.subject: Re: [EverQuest] GuComics.com
ygData.msgSnippet: I visited EQ Traders Corner (www.eqtraders.com) yesterday, and there was a message from the cartoonist saying that GU Comics had been discontinued as of August
ygData.messageBody:
I visited EQ Traders Corner (www.eqtraders.com) yesterday, and there was a
message from the cartoonist saying that GU Comics had been discontinued as
of August 29. The archives were still available, though. I agree, it was a
great comic.

----- Original Message -----
From: "Amanda" <ZeonChar@...>
To: <EverQuest@yahoogroups.com>
Sent: Sunday, September 02, 2001 8:03 PM
Subject: [EverQuest] GuComics.com


> Hey, does anyone know what's up with the Everquest-based comic
> GuComics.com? For a week or so now their page has been down and now
> it looks like the name isn't registered anymore. That was my favorite
> online comic next to Penny Arcade and I really want to know what
> happened! Anyone?
>
